data.description: Attention investors. Rare opportunity with both sides of duplex for sale. Excellent artisanship prevails with updated cabinets, fixtures, countertops, appliances, flooring, windows, and doors. New roof, oversized redwood decks and upgraded landscaping. Attached garage, large storage shed and fenced in backyard with Straight Creek flowing along back side of property. Refer to MLS#9210090 for details on unit A.
